reviews.review_text: first to comment?? cant believe no comments on this one. very nice job taper, cleaned it up quite a bit and it shows, sounds pretty good. better than 99% of the other dead auds on here. what a nice set too, always nice to hear cumberland blues. solid DS and eyes and good sugar magnolia always make for a good show
